[ c u d e m ]

CUDEM is a set of Python modules and console scripts for utilizing elevation data and Digital Elevation Models.

==============================================
Install via git and pip:
==============================================

 % git clone https:/github.com/ciresdem/cudem.git
 % cd cudem
 % pip install --user --upgrade ./

==============================================
Install via git and setup.py:
==============================================

 % git clone https://github.com/ciresdem/cudem.git
 % cd cudem
 % python setup.py build
 % sudo python setup.py install --record cudem.install

==============================================
Install via zip and setup.py:
==============================================

 % wget https://github.com/ciresdem/cudem/archive/master.zip
 % unzip master.zip
 % cd master
 % python setup.py build
 % sudo python setup.py install --record cudem.install

==============================================
Uninstall from setup.py:
==============================================
 
 % sudo python setup.py clean
 % sudo xargs rm -r < cudem.install

==============================================
Update with setup.py:
==============================================

 % git pull
 % sudo python setup.py clean
 % sudo xargs rm -r < cudem.install
 % python setup.py build
 % sudo python setup.py install --record cudem.install

